kanjipad (2.0.0-4) unstable; urgency=low

  * debian/control: Add Recommends: ttf-kochi-gothic | tff-kochi-mincho. It
    seems that these are good fonts for using Kanjipad with, and absence of
    appropriate fonts makes Kanjipad not very usable. Closes: #227874.

